  <brief_title>Study of Sutures Versus Staples for Skin Closure After Surgical Procedures of Hip</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparative Randomized Efficacy Study of Sutures Versus Staples in Hip Surgical Procedures</official_title>
  <sponsors>
